  "text": "This paper focuses on the original version of the MMA [CITATION_1] ) and its use for the simulation of rare events in slope stability analysis using the random finite element method. To avoid confusion between different versions of the MMA algorithm, it is repeated here. Given a link j > 1 in Markov chain k with samples from the conditional sampling space Ω (i) as a subspace from sampling space Ω (0) with standard normal prior distribution",
